# Installation instructions

1. Unpack the provided file (Seurat_2.2.0.tar.gz). Please note the directory where the contents are placed (for example : "~/Downloads/Seurat")

2. In R, install the devtools package 

  install.packages("devtools")

3. In R or RStudio : run

  devtools::install("~/Downloads/Seurat")
     
4. Load the Seurat package

  library(Seurat)


